# Presentation Layer (Apps)

## Locations
- `apps/web/` - Main web app
- `apps/api/` - Backend API
- `apps/admin/` - Admin dashboard

## Apps Structure
```
apps/<app>/
├── src/
│   ├── app/           # Routes/pages
│   ├── components/    # App-specific components
│   └── styles/        # App-specific styles
└── project.json       # Nx config
```

## Rules
- Apps are entry points only
- Import business logic from `@ryla/business`
- Import UI from `@ryla/ui`
- Import analytics from `@ryla/analytics`
- No business logic in apps

## API Controllers
- HTTP concerns only
- Extract to DTOs immediately
- Call services, no logic
- Standardized responses

## Responses
- Consistent structure
- No internal error exposure
- Appropriate HTTP status codes
